title: Excel 2016 Companion
description:
http://ititli.com/images/0unrble9q.jpg

Are you struggling with understanding Excel 2016 This book gives you the step by step tools to easily understand the software in no time! In fact, the Excel 2016 Companion is great for beginners or for the more experienced users, easy and simple to read format, step by step approach to quickly master Excel 2016, 20 CHAPTERS with EVERYTHING you need to know about Excel 2016, learn how to create an Excel workbook, work with formulas and functions, make charts and incorporate graphics, use advanced Excel features, learn Macros and much more!

Excel 2016 Companion: The Complete Guide for Doing Anything with Excel 2016
English | 15 September 2016 | 287 Pages | MOBI | 3.73 MB
